INSERT INTO [SPECTACLE INFO](spectacle_id, artwork_id, spectacle_name, language, duration, description, theater_id, age_restrictions_id) VALUES(13,5,'King Lear','russian','3:00:00','"King Lear" by Shakespeare was the first premiere on the opening after reconstruction of the historical stage of the Maly theatre on the Theatre square. The title role is assigned to the people''s artist of Russia Boris Nevzorov-the actor of bright colors and powerful temperament. Before him and his comrades on the stage is a very difficult task, because the complexity of the perception of this play is that there is no hope, optimism in looking at the essence of life. These are all great tragedies. It''s like they''re condemning people, human nature itself. As if they say that human genetics itself is self-destructive initially. The main question of the play, according to the Director Anton Yakovlev: "is it Possible to get out of this vicious circle? Can be he in love and faith?"But, alas, in "Lear" few who believe in something, except the right of power and strength.',47,4);
INSERT INTO [SPECTACLE INFO](spectacle_id, artwork_id, spectacle_name, language, duration, description, theater_id, age_restrictions_id) VALUES(14,6,'Macbeth','english','2:30:00','William Shakespeare''s tragedy in two acts. The performance is incredibly strong and burning. In "Macbeth" the Director saw a drama about the fate that pushes a person to the intended goal. Macbeth commits atrocities without respite and pause. Rock is omnipotent, it makes no sense to argue with him. This is the main idea of the play. Macbeth was king of Scotland from 1040. At the end of the 16th century, the king''s life became a legend. Shakespeare''s play is about excessive thirst for power. According to legend, king Duncan was the king of Scotland, and his relative Macbeth led the army on campaigns. In the forest, Macbeth met three witches, and after Duncan appointed him Thane (knight) of the two lands. The commander wanted to become king. And it was. In this he was helped by lady Macbeth because of the insidious plan. The son of king Duncan-Malcolm-opposed Macbeth and became the new king. The legend excited Shakespeare, he offered his interpretation. The evil lady Macbeth manipulates her husband, and offers to kill Duncan. Macbeth believes in prophecies, goes on about his wife to get the crown.',30,9);
