INSERT INTO [SPECTACLE INFO](spectacle_id, artwork_id, spectacle_name, language, duration, description, theater_id, age_restrictions_id) VALUES(95,28,'Suicide','russian','2:30:00','A person can not find a job for a year and is thinking about shooting himself. Here''s a story, and play his clowns. And terrible it becomes funny, and funny scary. The main character is sensitive and thin, he is a sad clown. He''s like a Pierrot that brings a smile to your sadness, it makes you grieve with him. So, what''s the cost of a suicide? A small man and a Comedy character on the verge of death suddenly grows into a big and tragic: "what is a second? Tick-tock... And is worth between teak and such a the wall. Yeah, the wall, the gun barrel... Tick-and here I am with myself, and with my wife, and with my mother-in-law, with the sun, with air and water, I understand that. So and here I am without a wife... although I without wife-this I understand, too,, I without mother-in-law... well, I even understand very well, but here I am without myself is I do not understand. How can I do without myself? You know, I? Me personally. Podsekalnikov. Man.»',16,5);
