INSERT INTO [SPECTACLE INFO](spectacle_id, artwork_id, spectacle_name, language, duration, description, theater_id, age_restrictions_id) VALUES(104,32,'Marriage','russian','3:00:00','Gogol''s "Marriage" was staged many times, but it is in the Moscow art theater that it looks as if it was written for this scene. Agafya performed Pegawai hilarious trying to marry Podkolesin in the performance of Sergei Doinikova, star of the TV series "Voronin". If you open a theatre poster, you''re sure to see the play Gogol "Marriage" is not in the same theatre of Moscow. This happened thanks to a simple, eternal, dynamic and very funny story. Succumbing to the Intrusive persuasion of his friend Kochkarev, a middle-aged nadvorny Advisor Podkolesin wooed to the merchant''s daughter, who sat in brides, Agafya Tikhonovna. He has to compete with the elderly and comical grooms, which he hopes to easily get around. The Director of the play, Igor Zolotovitsky, a famous actor of the Moscow art theater, works perfectly with his colleagues, showing their skills in the most favorable light. Zolotovitsky focuses all attention on the actors and their almost beneficial outputs, and such a game is always welcome and the actors and the audience. The Moscow art theatre. Chekhov-the legendary theater, on its stage you can see the leading Russian actors. The theater is headed by the national favorite Oleg Tabakov, who has earned the highest recognition not only because of the actor''s works, but also because he lit a huge number of stars as a teacher Of the Moscow art theater school. Today''s artists also teach a new generation of students.',46,5);
INSERT INTO [SPECTACLE INFO](spectacle_id, artwork_id, spectacle_name, language, duration, description, theater_id, age_restrictions_id) VALUES(105,32,'Marriage','russian','3:00:00','It is known that marriage for Gogol was synonymous with nightmare. The metaphorical play places the notion of a wife in a world of heavy delirium worthy of Kafka. Wife appears the "matter" (with hair), the commander of the infantry, the bell tower. A wife with a goose face everywhere, including in your pocket. The play reflects all Gogol''s thoughts concerning family life, all his neuroticism and fears. But it is difficult to argue with the fact that a forced Union can turn into a nightmare. In the uncomplicated plot of the play, the whole essence of Gogol''s creativity is manifested. According to Vladimir Nabokov, Gogol was inspired by the Muse of the absurd, and his Comedy is combined with tragedy. The protagonist of the encyclopedia of chambers, sees that around one solid "disgusting", he decides to change something, to do something and do something to save the situation... The act becomes a leap into the open window. In mark Zakharov''s characters become carnival masks that only in the hand of Gogol''s play. The author conveyed the hidden features of human nature, which all "lack of time" to get rid of, as brilliantly as his followers, Dostoevsky and Chekhov.',15,4);
