INSERT INTO [SPECTACLE INFO](spectacle_id, artwork_id, spectacle_name, language, duration, description, theater_id, age_restrictions_id) VALUES(138,51,'Oedipus Rex','russian','1:40:00','This is a very important project, as it combines two influential theatrical traditions: the skill of the Greek theater in the embodiment of the ancient tragedy and the Russian school of psychological theater. All theatres are now perceived as a single theatre. I do not feel any kind of gap, other theatrical space. It''s one. Pain, love, hatred - all of this we feel equally. Does pain have a nationality? I''m tired of comparisons. There is a world spirit of theater, there are no separate schools. There is a single school — the school of talent. That''s what I admit, it''s from God. I want to put on a play about the main thing — about human dignity, about honor, about a strong man, about a leader who was able to punish himself: to expel himself from the country, to leave the life of the poor. Today, this is almost there. All of them (leaders), in any case, for the most part, feel not guilty of anything. All justified. Everything is possible. Everything is allowed. I would like to raise the flag of honor and dignity of man.',14,4);
